item.title: NMB member rankings October edition
item.description: Intro This was the second time we have asked NMB fans from all around the world at the NMB discord server to submit their NMB member rankings. The first time was at the beginning of April. It was completely unorganized and the whole “project” happened only because I had the silly idea of collecting all the rankings everyone had unsuspectingly posted.
